sentence: And in Washington state, Rep. Jaime Herrera Beutler out-raised her Trump-backed opponent, Joe Kent, bringing in about $422,000 compared to his roughly $297,000 during that same period.
title: Republicans who impeached Trump outpace challengers in latest fundraising haul

sentence: Republican women's group Maggie's List has thrown its support behind Rep. Jaime Herrera Beutler (R-Wash.) as part of its latest round of endorsements first obtained by The Hill on Wednesday.
author: Julia Manchester
title: GOP women's group endorses Herrera Beutler in primary race
